{"tid":1885822,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香城教育電視今次想分析空氣清新機可唔可以隔走武漢肺炎病毒!!","createTime":"2020-02-18T14:17:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T08:17:41.000Z","uid":1806,"like":390,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"8e6fdaf00448d496ea74cfaf9086e3a0502ec43f","tid":1885822,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:17:37.000Z","msg":"大家好，又係我地香城教育電視，疫情日趨嚴重，再加上呢個無能嘅港共政府完全唔發放準確而有效嘅抗疫資訊，令香港市民越嚟越恐慌，謠言滿天飛。其中，好多人希望用空氣清新機&quot;除毒&quot;。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次我地就想探討一下究竟空氣清新機有冇用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先，全球嘅專家仍然未完全掌握武漢肺炎病毒嘅傳播方法。不過有明顯證據顯示，武漢肺炎同流感一樣，以飛沫為主要傳播方法。如果我哋借鑒流感嘅資料，病人5微米以下嘅飛沫，換言之PM2.5左右嘅飛沫，極有可能帶有病毒。<strong>[1]</strong> 所以，<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\"> 以下落嚟，我就會用&quot;空氣清新機能唔能夠過濾PM2.5&quot;嚟做空氣清新機可唔可以&quot;除毒&quot;嘅標準。</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n市面上嘅空氣清新機有兩類，<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">家用台式空氣清新機同隨身空氣清新機。</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">家用台式空氣清新機</span></strong>嘅原理主要用濾網隔走密室內嘅PM2.5微粒，包括上面提及嘅飛沫。所以家用台式空氣清新機對懸浮喺空氣嘅飛沫有一定嘅作用。[2] 但喺現實，亦有人會因為吸入病人直接噴出嘅飛沫而染病，呢個情況空氣清新機係無可能清除飛沫嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">隨身空氣清新</span></strong>機嘅原理主要係放出負離子，令PM2.5微粒帶電，然後吸附喺衣物上，減少吸入的機會。依照呢個原理我哋要考慮兩個情況：<strong>1.配戴者不斷移動。2.配戴者靜止。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>1.配戴者不斷移動嘅話，就算我哋假設呢個方法可行，淨化咗嘅空氣都唔會跟住配戴者移動（所以你後面果個先係得益者）。<br />\n<br />\n2.配戴者靜止嘅話，就好似家用台式空氣清新機一樣，有人會因為吸入病人直接噴出嘅飛沫而染病。請注意，負離子並唔係防護罩，唔會反彈或者阻隔直接噴出嘅飛沫。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隨身空氣清新機同家用台式空氣清新機唔同,佢對懸浮喺空氣嘅飛沫冇作用。市面上嘅隨身空氣清新機最高聲稱每立方厘米可產生69萬個負離子，另外<strong>[3] [4]</strong>嘅研究搵到，一個咳嗽，大約放出每立方厘米1000個飛沫，即係一個飛沫分到嘅負離子有690個。本身要負離子真係遇到飛沫，係極難嘅事。更加唔洗講遇到足夠嘅負電嚟吸附喺衣物上。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">TLDR: 家用台式空氣清新機喺較密閉嘅空間有少少作用，但係隨身空氣清新機就無乜用啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n另外，有唔少人留意到鑽石公主號郵輪有大批市民感染武漢肺炎，但响飛機就算有確診者，就未有聽過有呢個情況。有人提出疑問，點解飛機好似有咁大分別?<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個情況需要更多研究數據先可以揾到更確實既答案，但以目前有既資料同數據，可以簡單分析原因。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 首先參考美國聯邦航空管理局2013年既報告，新鮮空氣响高空係無菌既，而飛機既HEPA過濾器亦都有效去除細菌、病毒、灰塵同埋黴菌。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n機艙內既空氣循環有兩大特點：<br />\n<strong><blockquote><span style=\"color: orange;\">1.飛機有HEPA過濾器去過濾空氣，而空氣係由上而下咁吹，再响地下被吸走。<br />\n2.飛機內既空氣比較乾同凍，對細菌生長或者病毒存在比較不利。</span></blockquote></strong><br />\n<br />\n基於以上原因，飛機就可能暫時未有好似鑽石公主號郵輪既大規模感染。<br />\n<br />\n雖然係咁，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地仍然建議大家乘搭多人既交通（包括飛機）時，加強個人安全保護，進一步減低互相感染機會。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">康復香港 時代抗疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n相關新聞參考:<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><blockquote>專家：車船感染風險甚於飛機 - 20200211 - 國際 - 每日明報 - 明報新聞網<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20200211/s00014/1581359856543/%e5%b0%88%e5%ae%b6-%e8%bb%8a%e8%88%b9%e6%84%9f%e6%9f%93%e9%a2%a8%e9%9a%aa%e7%94%9a%e6%96%bc%e9%a3%9b%e6%a9%9f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200211%2Fs00014%2F1581359856543%2F%25e5%25b0%2588%25e5%25ae%25b6-%25e8%25bb%258a%25e8%2588%25b9%25e6%2584%259f%25e6%259f%2593%25e9%25a2%25a8%25e9%259a%25aa%25e7%2594%259a%25e6%2596%25bc%25e9%25a3%259b%25e6%25a9%259f&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmhvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=33914dd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200211%2Fs00014%2F1581359856543%2F%25e5%25b0%2588%25e5%25ae%25b6-%25e8%25bb%258a%25e8%2588%25b9%25e6%2584%259f%25e6%259f%2593%25e9%25a2%25a8%25e9%259a%25aa%25e7%2594%259a%25e6%2596%25bc%25e9%25a3%259b%25e6%25a9%259f&h=52614ef1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20200211/s00014/1581359856543/%e5%b0%88%e5%ae%b6-%e8%bb%8a%e8%88%b9%e6%84%9f%e6%9f%93%e9%a2%a8%e9%9a%aa%e7%94%9a%e6%96%bc%e9%a3%9b%e6%a9%9f</a><br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎｜「世界夢」餘波】乘客嘆被當生化炸彈 工程專家：空調系統可能是播毒關鍵<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com//realtime/article/20200212/724665\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2F%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200212%2F724665&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmhvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=9a0c2f52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2F%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200212%2F724665&h=7739f9d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com//realtime/article/20200212/724665</a></blockquote></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>參考資料:</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">[1] Milton DK, Fabian MP, Cowling BJ, Grantham ML, McDevitt JJ. Influenza virus aerosols in human exhaled breath: particle size, culturability, and effect of surgical masks. PLoS Pathog. 2013;9(3):e1003205. doi:10.1371/journal.ppat.1003205<br />\n<br />\n[2] Vyas S, Srivastav N, Spears D. An Experiment with Air Purifiers in Delhi during Winter 2015-2016. PLoS One. 2016;11(12):e0167999. Published 2016 Dec 15. doi:10.1371/journal.pone.0167999<br />\n<br />\n[3] Hart JF, Ward TJ, Spear TM, Rossi RJ, Holland NN, Loushin BG. Evaluating the effectiveness of a commercial portable air purifier in homes with wood burning stoves: a preliminary study. J Environ Public Health. 2011;2011:324809. doi:10.1155/2011/324809<br />\n<br />\n[4] Yang, Shinhao &amp; Lee, Grace &amp; Chen, Cheng-Min &amp; Wu, Chih-Cheng &amp; Yu, Kuo-Pin. (2007). The Size and Concentration of Droplets Generated by Coughing in Human Subjects. Journal of aerosol medicine : the official journal of the International Society for Aerosols in Medicine. 20. 484-94. 10.1089/jam.2007.0610. </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>如想支持我地既工作，可以透過<br />\n<blockquote>Buy me a coffee捐款（以美金結算）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<a href=\"https://www.buymeacoffee.com/hkgetv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buymeacoffee.com%2Fhkgetv&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmhvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=04516e2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.buymeacoffee.com/hkgetv</a><br />\n或<br />\n眾籌連結（以港幣結算）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<a href=\"https://goget.fund/2MOT9co\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoget.fund%2F2MOT9co&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmhvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=f578e31f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goget.fund/2MOT9co</a></blockquote></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">HKGETV Social Media Platform<br />\n<strong><blockquote>YouTube Channel: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w/featured\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w%2Ffeatured&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmhvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=af539eb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w/featured</a><br />\nOur Facebook Page: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKGETV/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKGETV%2F&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmhvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=739ca106\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKGETV/</a><br />\nOur Instagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/HKGETV/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2FHKGETV%2F&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmhvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=7cc9e821\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/HKGETV/</a><br />\nOur Twitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hkgetv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.l