f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點可能有用"},{"pid":"88819f11926d11676c5d973a442799a813806db9","tid":1885822,"uid":189626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:22:55.000Z","msg":"Sharp 空氣清新機既負離子技術聲稱可以殺病毒，點睇？"},{"pid":"8f6048e643486ab4189d5e4dffa9e677e35f4a3f","tid":1885822,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:24:16.000Z","msg":"其實隻武漢肺炎病毒好似係 &lt;0.1&mu;m，<br />\n你有 PM 0.1&mu;m 都未必有用，一樣穿過<br />\nPM 2.5&mu;m 更加唔使講，冇用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過隻病毒都係依附口水飛沬傳播，而飛沬應該係 3-5&mu;m，<br />\n應該有少少用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/utXbrCj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FutXbrCj.jpg&h=2778aafd&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/79yh6CA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F79yh6CA.png&h=52e576a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有錯請指正<br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n口罩正確戴法、尺寸挑選你知道嗎？日本「防疫教學」一次對抗武漢肺炎、流感病毒<br />\n文／Japaholic 攝影／Japaholic2020-02-03<br />\n<a href=\"https://playing.ltn.com.tw/article/19055/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplaying.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2F19055%2F1&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmhvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=67cd3cdf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplaying.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2F19055%2F1&h=e026c5ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://playing.ltn.com.tw/article/19055/1</a>"},{"pid":"f7766d78a7f9d42afc5d9856b44d8b9106d7b001","tid":1885822,"uid":135554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:25:04.000Z","msg":"好文必推"},{"pid":"361bae4dfc94e0471d2d4e44c282f9dc2a43a2f0","tid":1885822,"uid":123308,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"04c4e6b916a28f11419a7e0b4b47ec47a9bd04e2","tid":1885822,"uid":138064,"like":50,"dislike":2,"scor