02-18T14:47:39.000Z","msg":"只睇家用機<br />\n負離子遇到病毒從而殺菌的機率係唔係極少<br />\n咁負離子功能係唔係弊(臭氧)多於利<br />\n<br />\n利申 覺得冇咩用，不過見佢吸到下塵就由佢"},{"pid":"6dd8b07ffc7f9d2e97478a437715f791b9c32dab","tid":1885822,"uid":26449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:49:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ea354b092378f57e51d30d932b1cfbb46d1dea5","tid":1885822,"uid":85822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:54:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a75ec36cebb2d62cc8a31b198a2e3debf0a4bcd","tid":1885822,"uid":4204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:58:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac74045ae165005dea6c0cd545b40cafccc33f5f","tid":1885822,"uid":189650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T15:00:03.000Z","msg":"多謝涼茶團隊，終於有篇文可以畀我呀媽睇，睇吓勸唔勸掂佢<br />\n成日話啲乜嘢淨化器清新機今次好有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(戴好個口罩加個眼罩好過啦)<br />\n<br />\n不過第二點有啲問題<br />\n「2.飛機內既空氣比較乾同凍，對細菌生長或者病毒存在比較不利。」<br />\n唔係話病毒喺濕熱環境比較不利咩？<br />\n<br />\n搵到篇文講關於流感病毒喺潮濕下不利嘅原因，講到一個例外係潮濕嘅話病毒會黐喺室內更多表面上面，增加接觸傳播可能，但加濕空氣可以有效預防流感病毒，唔知可唔可以apply落去呢隻武漢肺炎病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n流感在冬天傳播的真實原因<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/ukchina/trad/vert_fut/2015/10/151027_vert_fut_winter_flu_germs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fukchina%2Ftrad%2Fvert_fut%2F2015%2F10%2F151027_vert_fut_winter_flu_germs&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmhvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=157cc4b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fukchina%2Ftrad%2Fvert_fut%2F2015%2F10%2F151027_vert_fut_winter_flu_germs&h=024388e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/ukchina/trad/vert_fut/2015/10/151027_vert_fut_winter_flu_germs</a>"},{"pid":"2e83bcd89c14ab92edfa19905cf3b0aafaf4ab32","tid":1885822,"uid":45684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":